dct_description_sm: 2 bar scales on map, given in "Milles com. de Germanie" and "Verstes ou Milles de Moscovie."
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margin.
Index in upper right, and at bottom: Table des principales Provinces de cette Carte.
Descriptive text in upper right, and at bottom.
From Châtelain's Atlas historique, Vol. IV, Amsterdam, 1705-1720.
